CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 5, 1955, pg. 14B, reads: "African Premier Visits City - The Hon. Nnamdi Azikiwe, Prime Minister of Eastern Nigeria, West Africa, was in city, the guest of The Courier, Thursday, to advance plans for the establishment of the University of Nigeria..."
TitMainTitle: Eastern Nigerian Prime Minister Nnamdi Azikiwe wearing agbada and cap, shaking hands with Florence Bluett, with other women, possibly including "Muz" third from left, and man, in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper office
